      <div class="prob-card"><div class="prob-n">05</div><div class="prob-ttl">ERP Data Silos</div><div class="prob-body">Buyers and suppliers worked from conflicting PO versions. ERP systems didn't sync. The "single source of truth" was whoever had the most recent email. Disputes wasted days of operational time.</div></div>
