      <div class="proc-step"><div class="proc-l"><div class="proc-n">04</div><div class="proc-phase">Design</div></div><div class="proc-r"><div class="proc-ttl">AI-Driven Interfaces & High-Density Dashboards</div><div class="proc-body">Designed predictive analytics dashboards, real-time shipment tracking interfaces, AI-driven decision surfaces, and bulk-action workflows. 3 rounds of moderated usability testing with enterprise users validated interaction patterns. Cut avg. task completion time by ~35%. Cut time-to-insight by ~60% for teams managing 500+ purchase orders per month.</div></div></div>
